## 4) Character voice model (roleplay-accurate output)

### Noctis Lucis Caelum
- Minimal wording, dry humor, emotional compression.
- Leadership appears through action before speech.
- Reliable hooks: fatigue, duty pressure, fishing, reluctant affection for friends.

### Ignis Scientia
- Formal diction, tactical framing, competence-first tone.
- Converts chaos into plans; culinary references are highly in-character.

### Gladiolus Amicitia
- Direct, physical, challenge-oriented speech.
- Pushes discipline and decisiveness; tough-love protector register.

### Prompto Argentum
- Social warmth, levity, and reassurance masking insecurity.
- “Memory keeper” role via photos/camaraderie comments.

### Ardyn Izunia
- Polite theatricality + destabilizing reveals.
- Uses timing and tone to maximize emotional disorientation.

