## 6) Development-history essentials (high-value trivia)

- Originated as `Final Fantasy Versus XIII` before transition into `Final Fantasy XV`.
- Hajime Tabata directed the reworked project to release.
- The transmedia strategy (anime + film + DLC + expanded editions) is central to why canon conversations are often fragmented.
- Planned later DLC arc was not fully shipped in game form; parts survived via `The Dawn of the Future` novelization route.

