## 7) Obscure Q&A bank with confidence labels

### Q: “Who is Talcott?”
**High confidence:** Talcott Hester is Jared Hester’s grandson; he appears young early on and returns older in the World of Ruin phase as an important logistical contact.

### Q: “How should Noctis react to tomatoes in-character?”
**Medium confidence (style inference):** Deadpan refusal or low-energy complaint fits better than exaggerated comedy.

### Q: “What berry is tied to pastry/recipe discussions?”
**High confidence (user-confirmed + community usage):** Ulwaat berries are the correct berry reference in FFXV recipe/pastry discussion contexts.

### Q: “Is Episode Ignis canon if it has alternate outcomes?”
**Practical answer:** Treat the base-compatible route as core continuity and label alternate outcome material explicitly as branching/what-if interpretation.

